Comment.val: /* Monitor op tabel 'JMS_FAILED_MESSAGES' Mogelijkheid voor opnieuw aanbieden. */

ExpSyntax.val: 'Datum t/m moet gelijk of groter zijn dan Datum vanaf !'

Text.val: The Foreign key constraint in the database will delete the 'JMS_FAILED_MESSAGES' record when the metadata is deleted.
If no metadata is found the 'JMS_FAILED_MESSAGE' record wil be deleted in here via force record delete!

SQL_STMT_U.val: select distinct f.jfm_push_queue_id, nvl(p.puqu_description, 'Unknown Id: ' || to_char(f.jfm_push_queue_id)) from jms_failed_messages f left outer join sc_push_queues p on p.puqu_id = f.jfm_push_queue_id order by 2
